# Authors

This project is maintained by the Vernam Mail team.

## Maintainer

Imporon Inc. (operating as Vernam Mail)
Contact: `security@vernammail.com`

## Acknowledgments

The protocol's hybrid KEM construction draws on work by:

- The NIST PQC standardization team (FIPS 203 ML-KEM)
- Daniel J. Bernstein and the X25519 designers (RFC 7748)
- Hugo Krawczyk and Pasi Eronen (HKDF, RFC 5869)
- The IETF CFRG and authors of RFC 9180 (HPKE) for hybrid construction patterns

External contributors will be listed here as the project grows.
